creator: Kyrylo Bespoludin
descriptionHtml:
Prove your zombie-slaying skills in an action-packed shooter with RPG elements. But it ain’t’ a cakewalk — zombies can wield guns they are pretty good at it, so beware! You will need to actively use weapon perks and cover to go through locations full of vile zombies and reach a safe haven.

- Choose your special tactics against each zombie type
- Upgrade up your skills and abilities
- Craft new equipment to deal with the advanced hordes of zombies
- Interesting boss mechanics
- Upgrade your equipment for each slot
- Attach weapon accessories for a more convenient shooting
- Challenging endgame content
- Use cover to your advantage
descriptionShort: Save the planet from being captured by zombies
